rc=\"img/uploads/20180929095051k7qu4KmsSxERtFin.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929095051lXyUsxFhMNPgac2f.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929095051XHh8PlZ3ENTeJGCu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929095051GCX8f4j9wmetax7y.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><strong>Balmain 2019 春季成衣系列：</strong></p><p>几乎每套服装都呈现出强烈的雕塑感。很显然，创意总监&nbsp;Olivier Rousteing 并没在这个成衣系列中考虑太多实穿性的问题——这里是巴黎，每套服装展示出的缝纫工艺和对艺术性的追求应该满足“巴黎”对高级时尚的定义。</p><p>“我对扮酷没什么兴趣。我在乎的是 100 年后人们是否还会记得我的所说、所做、所为。”Olivier Rousteing 说。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103322hCeW5BJm8XPgNruv.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103322sLikyEvAVO7BxKJd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103321BHCO39UJcySPXdkM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103321z9egL7J8qnNZ6rtW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103321rz9h7l1IQ56uDVvT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103322LYxQed2IEoHtrf36.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103322JQliCUovjwtpKDN0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180929103322O2FQNnLCRlkxhTeX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500732\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> 